'''César Saúl Huerta Valera''' (born 3 December 2000) is a Mexican professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Winger (association football)|winger]] for [[Belgian Pro League]] club [[R.S.C. Anderlecht|Anderlecht]] and the [[Mexico national football team|Mexico national team]].<ref>{{cite web |url= https://ligamx.net/cancha/jugador/110948/eyJpZENsdWIiOiAxMjA0M30=/cesar-saul-huerta-valera |title=César Saúl Huerta Valera|publisher= LIGA BBVA Bancomer MX |website= LigaMX.net|accessdate= 18 December 2018}}</ref>

==Club career==
===Early career===
Huerta's career began at the youth academy of his hometown club, [[C.D. Guadalajara|Guadalajara]].<ref>{{cite web |url= https://www.chivasdecorazon.com.mx/es/noticias/31056/El-perfil-de-la-cantera-Csar-Huerta |title= Cantera Chivas Cesar Huerta|publisher= Salvador Pacheco|website= chivasdecorazon |accessdate= 24 August 2020|language=Spanish}}</ref> He made his professional debut on 10 November 2018, coming off the bench in a league match against [[Club León|León]].<ref>{{cite web |url= https://chivaspasion.bolavip.com/ligamx/Orgullo-Tapatio-Cesar-Huerta-hizo-su-debut-oficial-en-Primera-Division-20181111-0008.html |title= Cesar Huerta Debut|publisher= Chivas Passion |website= chivaspassion.mx |date= 11 November 2018|accessdate= 24 August 2020|language=Spanish}}</ref>

After a brief spell with [[Ascenso MX]] club [[Atlético Zacatepec]],<ref>{{cite web|title=César Huerta quiere regresar a Chivas como goleador|url=https://espndeportes.espn.com/futbol/mexico/nota/_/id/5347766/cesar-huerta-quiere-regresar-a-chivas-como-goleador|work=ESPN Deportes|date=4 March 2019|language=Spanish}}</ref> Huerta joined [[Monarcas Morelia]] on loan.<ref>{{cite web|title=Chivas no quiere sorpresas y presta a César Huerta al Morelia sin opción a compra|url=https://www.mediotiempo.com/futbol/liga-mx/chivas-presta-cesar-huerta-morelia-opcion-compra|work=Medio Tiempo|date=3 January 2020|language=Spanish}}</ref> Six months later, he moved to [[Mazatlán F.C.|Mazatlán]] following the franchise's relocation.<ref name=Marshall>{{cite web|last=Marshall|first=Tom|title=Liga MX club Morelia officially moves to Mazatlan |url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/mexican-liga-bbva-mx/story/4105489/liga-mx-club-morelia-moves-to-mazatlan|website=ESPN|accessdate=9 June 2020|date=2 June 2020}}</ref>

On 27 July 2020, Mazatlán made their debut in an official match, with Huerta scoring the very first official goal for the club.<ref>{{cite web |title=Mazatlán FC vs. Puebla - Resumen de Juego - 27 julio, 2020 |url=https://www.espn.com.mx/futbol/partido?juegoId=573974 |website=ESPN |accessdate=28 July 2020 |language=Spanish}}</ref>

===UNAM===
Upon returning to Guadalajara, Huerta was unable to secure a place in the starting lineup and requested a transfer. On 1 June 2022, [[Club Universidad Nacional|Universidad Nacional]] reached an agreement to sign him.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://espndeportes.espn.com/futbol/mexico/nota/_/id/12844172/pumas-vs-chivas-jornada-17-apertura-2023-cesar-chino-huerta|title=César Huerta, de ser abucheado y agredido, a figura en Pumas|website=ESPN Deportes|language=es|date=11 November 2023}}</ref>

===Anderlecht===
On 10 January 2025, Huerta joined [[Belgian Pro League]] club [[R.S.C. Anderlecht|Anderlecht]] on a four-year deal.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rsca.be/en/Cesar-Huerta|title=César Huerta, RSCA's new signing|website=Royal Sporting Club Anderlecht|date=10 January 2025}}</ref>

On 19 January, Huerta made his debut with the club in a league match against [[K.V. Kortrijk|Kortrijk]], coming on as a substitute and scoring in a 2–0 win.<ref>https://prosoccerwire.usatoday.com/story/sports/2025/01/19/chino-huerta-scores-goal-anderlecht-debut/77826981007/</ref>

On 4 May, Huerta was in the starting line-up that played the [[2025 Belgian Cup final]] against [[Club Brugge KV|Club Brugge]], where he was substituted off during the second half as Anderlecht lost 2–1.<ref>https://espndeportes.espn.com/futbol/nota/_/id/15137255/brujas-vs-anderlecht-final-copa-belgica-cesar-huerta-resumen</ref>

==International career==
===Youth===
Huerta was called up by [[Mario Arteaga]] to be part of the squad that participated at the [[2017 CONCACAF U-17 Championship]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Lista la convocatoria del Tri Sub-17 para el Premundial|url=https://www.marca.com/claro-mx/futbol/seleccion-mx/2017/04/16/58f3d58dca47416d438b4615.html|work=Marca|date=16 April 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref> and subsequently won. He was also called up to participate at the [[2017 FIFA U-17 World Cup]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Esta será la Selección Mexicana que participará en el Mundial Sub-17|url=https://www.telemundodeportes.com/copa-mundial-sub-17-de-la-fifa-india-2017/esta-sera-la-seleccion-mexicana-que-participara-en-el-mundial-sub-17|work=Telemundo Deportes|date=14 September 2017|language=Spanish}}</ref>

===Senior===
In August 2023, Huerta received his first call-up to the [[Mexico national football team|senior national team]] by manager [[Jaime Lozano]], for two [[Exhibition game|friendly matches]] against [[Australia men's national soccer team|Australia]] and [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=29 August 2023 |title=Lista de convocados por Jaime Lozano para integrar la Selección Nacional de México |url=https://miseleccion.mx/noticias/5112/Lista-de-convocados-por-Jaime-Lozano-para-integrar-la-Selecci%C3%B3n-Nacional-de-M%C3%A9xico |access-date=2 September 2023 |website=[[Mexican Football Federation]] |language=es-MX}}</ref>

Huerta made his senior debut for [[Mexico national football team|Mexico]] on 9 September 2023, in a friendly match against [[Australia men's national soccer team|Australia]], entering in the second half for [[Alexis Vega (footballer, born 1997)|Alexis Vega]] at the 60th minute and later scoring the 2–2 equalizer towards the end of the match in the 83rd minute.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/report/_/gameId/683508|title=Mexico fights back to 2-2 draw with Socceroos|date=9 September 2023|work=[[ESPN.com]]|first=Cesar|last=Hernández|access-date=9 September 2023}}</ref>

